                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-7 mb-4">
                    AKSAM ASSURANCES SARL AU, au capital de 10.000 €,
                    située au 10 Rue de Penthièvre, 75008 Paris.
                </p>

                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border">SIRET : 84065346300033</div>
                    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border">RCS : 840 653 463</div>
                    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border">ORIAS : 180 074 24</div>
                    <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-4 border">RC professionnelle conforme</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# CARD #}
            <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-white/50 hover:shadow-2xl transition duration-500">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🌐 Hébergeur</h2>

                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-7">
                    Le site est hébergé par <strong>NAMECHEAP</strong>,
